data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home in the Heart of Anatolia Community! Nestled on a spacious corner lot, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath remodeled home offers the perfect blend of modern living and timeless beauty. The open-concept living area is the heart of this home, boasting abundant natural light, and seamless flow from the living room to the kitchen and dining areas. This inviting space is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining.The fully remodeled kitchen is a chef's dream come true. It features top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a Fulgor Milano Range with professional grade dual fuel (gas range and electric oven), gorgeous quartz counters, and a beautiful large center island with breakfast bar seating. The generous master bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with an en-suite bathroom, complete with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. This home has been remodeled with attention to detail. Upgrades include newer flooring, fresh paint, updated fixtures, and modern finishes throughout. As a resident of the Anatolia HOA you'll enjoy access to a range of amenities, including parks, a clubhouse, pools, and more. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this stunning home your own!
